## 🗺️ Visualizing the Attack Chain

### 🕵️ The Logic Flow
```text
Phase 1: The Extraction (Stealthy)
[ 👤 Attacker (Low Priv) ] --> Asks DC for SQL Service Ticket  --> [ 🏰 Domain Controller ]
[ 🏰 Domain Controller ]   --> Encrypts ticket with SQL Hash   --> [ 👤 Attacker ]
[ 👤 Attacker ]            --> Saves encrypted ticket to disk  --> [ 📄 hashes.txt ]

Phase 2: The Crack (Offline)
[ 📄 hashes.txt ]          --> Loaded into GPU / Hashcat       --> [ 💻 Attacker Host ]
[ 💻 Attacker Host ]       --> Brute-forces RC4 encryption     --> [ 🔓 Plaintext Password ]

